          <a href="/blog/how-to-become-a-product-manager">How to become a Product Manager (for college students)</a>
        </h1>
        <div class="meta article-meta">
          <span class="date"><time class="published dt-published" datetime="2016-04-13" itemprop="datePublished">April 13, 2016</time></span>
